# CommonsBase_Std

## Overview

Precompiled, relocatable cross-platform userland utilities (coreutils, fd, 7-Zip, msiextract, and toybox) packaged as dk assets for macOS, Linux, and Windows.

`CommonsBase_Std` assembles upstream command-line tools into per-slot dk
objects so downstream packages get a consistent `coreutils`, `fd`, `7zz`,
`msiextract`, and `toybox` across every supported ABI. Each tool is
fetched from its official release, verified by SHA-256, and shipped
alongside its verbatim upstream license file.

